metadata.name: DIGITAL_SKULL_01
metadata.description:
I am interested in the meaning of death and how it is presented in different cultures.

Skulls as a tribute to life remind us of our mortality and the value of each moment.

We are fleeting and also eternal.

----

The first owner has the option of a signed print 24x24in on 300gsm hot press paper.
Contact me on Twitter after purchase.
